    dc:title "Morphological revision of the hyperdiverse Brueelia - complex (Insecta: Phthiraptera: Ischnocera: Philopteridae) with new taxa, checklists and generic key" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.883224>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.883228>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.883222>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.883226>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.883171> ;
